<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<task id="R2-003" project="SprkChat Platform Enhancement R2">
  <metadata>
    <title>Create playbook-embeddings AI Search Index and BFF Embedding Generation Utility</title>
    <status>pending</status>
    <phase>1</phase>
    <tags>ai, azure-ai, search, foundation, bff-api</tags>
    <estimated-effort>medium</estimated-effort>
    <parallel-group>none</parallel-group>
    <parallel-safe>false</parallel-safe>
    <rigor-hint>FULL</rigor-hint>
    <rigor-reason>Creates new Azure infrastructure (AI Search index) AND new BFF C# service code for embedding generation. Tags include ai and bff-api; creates new .cs files; 9+ steps. PlaybookDispatcher (R2-015) depends on this index existing and the embedding utility being callable.</rigor-reason>
    <dependencies>[]</dependencies>
  </metadata>

  <prompt>
    Create a dedicated Azure AI Search index named `playbook-embeddings` for semantic playbook matching, and implement the BFF utility that generates embeddings from playbook content and indexes them into this index.

    **Index schema** (`infrastructure/ai-search/playbook-embeddings.json`):
    - `id` (Edm.String, key)
    - `playbookId` (Edm.String, filterable, retrievable)
    - `playbookName` (Edm.String, searchable, retrievable)
    - `description` (Edm.String, searchable, retrievable)
    - `triggerPhrases` (Collection(Edm.String), searchable, retrievable)
    - `recordType` (Edm.String, filterable, retrievable)
    - `entityType` (Edm.String, filterable, retrievable)
    - `tags` (Collection(Edm.String), filterable, retrievable)
    - `contentVector3072` (Collection(Edm.Single), 3072 dimensions, HNSW vector profile — text-embedding-3-large)

    **BFF embedding generation utility** (`src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/Services/Ai/PlaybookEmbeddingService.cs`):
    - Method: `IndexPlaybookAsync(string playbookId, PlaybookEmbeddingDocument document, CancellationToken ct)`
    - Generates embedding by calling Azure OpenAI `text-embedding-3-large` with content composed of: playbookName + description + triggerPhrases (joined) + tags
    - Uploads document with embedding to the `playbook-embeddings` index via Azure AI Search SDK
    - Method: `SearchPlaybooksAsync(string query, string? recordTypeFilter, int topK, CancellationToken ct)` — vector search against the index, returns `PlaybookSearchResult[]`
    - Does NOT register in DI — instantiated via factory per ADR-010 DI budget constraint
  </prompt>

  <role>Senior full-stack developer with Dataverse and Azure AI expertise</role>

  <goal>
    The `playbook-embeddings` index exists in Azure AI Search (`spaarke-search-dev`) with the correct schema and vector configuration. `PlaybookEmbeddingService.cs` compiles cleanly and provides both indexing and search methods. The index is queryable via vector similarity search using `text-embedding-3-large` embeddings.
  </goal>

  <inputs>
    <file purpose="Project specification — playbook embedding index design, dedicated index decision, NFR-04">projects/ai-sprk-chat-platform-enhancement-r2/spec.md</file>
    <file purpose="Project AI context — DI budget constraint, ADR-010 factory instantiation pattern">projects/ai-sprk-chat-platform-enhancement-r2/CLAUDE.md</file>
    <file purpose="Azure AI resources — AI Search endpoint, OpenAI endpoint, model deployments">docs/architecture/auth-AI-azure-resources.md</file>
    <file purpose="SSE and AI Search patterns — how existing search services are structured">../.claude/patterns/ai/streaming-endpoints.md</file>
    <file purpose="ADR-013 — extend BFF, SpeFileStore, ChatHostContext flow">../.claude/adr/ADR-013-ai-architecture.md</file>
    <file purpose="ADR-014 — no streaming token cache, version cache keys, tenant scope">../.claude/adr/ADR-014-ai-caching.md</file>
  </inputs>

  <constraints>
    <constraint source="ADR-013">MUST extend Sprk.Bff.Api — no separate AI microservice. PlaybookEmbeddingService lives in Services/Ai/</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-010">DI registrations currently at 16 (over ≤15 limit). PlaybookEmbeddingService MUST NOT be registered in DI directly — use factory instantiation pattern: SprkChatAgentFactory.ResolveTools() or a dedicated PlaybookEmbeddingServiceFactory that creates instances without AddSingleton/AddScoped</constraint>
    <constraint source="ADR-014">MUST version cache keys when caching embedding results. MUST scope cache keys by tenant. MUST NOT cache streaming tokens (not applicable here — embeddings are cacheable final values)</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec">Dedicated index — separate from document RAG index (spaarke-rag-knowledge, spaarke-rag-documents). Do NOT share schema with existing indexes.</constraint>
    <constraint source="spec NFR-04">Vector search + LLM refinement MUST complete within 2 seconds total for playbook matching</constraint>
    <constraint source="docs/architecture/auth-AI-azure-resources.md">MUST use spaarke-search-dev AI Search service and spaarke-openai-dev Azure OpenAI deployment. Model: text-embedding-3-large (3072 dimensions)</constraint>
  </constraints>

  <knowledge>
    <files>
      <file>projects/ai-sprk-chat-platform-enhancement-r2/spec.md</file>
      <file>projects/ai-sprk-chat-platform-enhancement-r2/CLAUDE.md</file>
      <file>docs/architecture/auth-AI-azure-resources.md</file>
      <file>.claude/patterns/ai/streaming-endpoints.md</file>
