    <skill>.claude/skills/task-execute/SKILL.md</skill>
    <protocol>No dependencies — can start immediately in parallel with R2-001 and R2-002. Read SemanticSearchService.cs FIRST to understand the existing Azure AI Search pattern used in the BFF before writing new code.</protocol>
